// RunRootCmd entrypoint of the root command
func RunRootCmd() error {
	viper.AutomaticEnv()
	viper.SetEnvKeyReplacer(strings.NewReplacer(".", "_", "-", "_"))

	cmd := &cobra.Command{
		Use:     "liveflights",
		Short:   "[Aviation] Live Flights Service",
		Version: "1.0.0",
	}

	cmd.AddCommand(serve.New())
	cmd.AddCommand(scraper.New())
	cmd.AddCommand(data_processor.New())

	cmd.PersistentFlags().Bool("logging.debug", false, "Whether to emit debug level logs or not.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("logging.encoding", "json", "The log encoding strategy.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().StringP("app.name", "n", "[Aviation] Live Flights", "The application name.")

	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("aws.access-key-id", "", "The AWS access key ID.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("aws.secret-access-key", "", "The AWS secret access key.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("aws.session-token", "", "The AWS session token.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("aws.endpoint-url", "", "The AWS endpoint.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("aws.region", "", "The AWS region.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().Bool("aws.s3.use-path-style", false, "Whether to use path style URLs when calling S3 APIs.")

	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.name", "live_flights", "DB name for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.host", "localhost", "Host name for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.user", "root", "User for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.password", "example", "Password for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().Int("mongodb.port", 27019, "Port for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.replica-set", "rs0", "Replica set name for the database")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("mongodb.uri", "", "URI for the database")

	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("cache.host", "localhost", "The cache host.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().Int("cache.port", 6379, "The cache port.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("cache.user", "default", "The cache user.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().String("cache.password", "", "The cache password.")
	cmd.PersistentFlags().Duration("cache.ttl.default", 7*(24*time.Hour), "The default ttl for cache items.")

	_ = viper.BindPFlags(cmd.PersistentFlags())

	return cmd.Execute()
}

package core

import (
	"time"
)

// ClassificationComparator is a comparator for airlines and airports classification
type ClassificationComparator int8

const (
	// ClassificationGreaterComparator is a comparator for greater than
	ClassificationGreaterComparator ClassificationComparator = iota + 1
	// ClassificationEqualComparator is a comparator for equal
	ClassificationEqualComparator
	// ClassificationLesserComparator is a comparator for lesser than
	ClassificationLesserComparator
)

type (
	Classification struct {
		C          int8
		Comparator ClassificationComparator
	}

	Airline struct {
		ID             string
		Designator     string
		IATA           *string
		ICAO           *string
		Classification int64
	}

	Airport struct {
		ID             string
		Designator     string
		IATA           *string
		ICAO           *string
		Classification int64
	}

	LiveFlight struct {
		ID                    string
		FlightID              *string
		FlightNumber          string
		AirlineDesignator     string
		AirlineClassification int
		DepartureTime         time.Time
		DepartureAirportIATA  string
		DepartureAirportICAO  string
		ArrivalAirportIATA    string
		ArrivalAirportICAO    string
		Position              Coordinate
		Altitude              float64
		HeadingDirection      float64
		GroundSpeed           float64
		VerticalSpeed         float64
		Squawk                int
		Tracks                []TrackPoint
		CreatedAt             time.Time
		UpdatedAt             time.Time
	}

	Coordinate struct {
		Lat float64
		Lon float64
	}

	TrackPoint struct {
		LiveFlightID     string
		Position         Coordinate
		Altitude         float64
		HeadingDirection float64
		GroundSpeed      float64
		VerticalSpeed    float64
		Squawk           int
		CreatedAt        time.Time
	}

	LiveFlightUpdate struct {
		ID                   string
		FlightNumber         string
		AirlineDesignator    string
		DepartureTime        time.Time
		DepartureAirportIATA string
		DepartureAirportICAO string
		ArrivalAirportIATA   string
		ArrivalAirportICAO   string
		Position             Coordinate
		Altitude             float64
		HeadingDirection     float64
		GroundSpeed          float64
		VerticalSpeed        float64
		Squawk               int
		CreatedAt            time.Time
	}

	BoundingBox struct {
		TopLeft     *Coordinate
		BottomRight *Coordinate
	}
)

type (
	EnrichedFlightData struct {
		LiveFlightID   string
		FlightID       *string
		Classification int64
	}
)

type (
	FlightsWithin struct {
		BoundingBox           *BoundingBox
		MaxAge                time.Duration
		AirlineClassification *Classification
	}
)

func (u *liveFlight) toDomain() *core.LiveFlight {
	coord := coordinateFromPoint(&u.Position)

	return &core.LiveFlight{
		ID:                    u.ID,
		FlightID:              u.FlightID,
		FlightNumber:          u.FlightNumber,
		AirlineDesignator:     u.AirlineDesignator,
		AirlineClassification: u.AirlineClassification,
		DepartureTime:         u.DepartureTime,
		DepartureAirportICAO:  u.DepartureAirportICAO,
		DepartureAirportIATA:  u.DepartureAirportIATA,
		ArrivalAirportICAO:    u.ArrivalAirportICAO,
		ArrivalAirportIATA:    u.ArrivalAirportIATA,
		Position:              coord,
		CreatedAt:             u.CreatedAt,
		UpdatedAt:             u.UpdatedAt,
	}
}

func (tp *trackPoint) toDomain() core.TrackPoint {
	return core.TrackPoint{
		LiveFlightID:     tp.LiveFlightID,
		Position:         coordinateFromPoint(&tp.Position),
		Altitude:         tp.Altitude,
		HeadingDirection: tp.HeadingDirection,
		GroundSpeed:      tp.GroundSpeed,
		VerticalSpeed:    tp.VerticalSpeed,
		Squawk:           tp.Squawk,
		CreatedAt:        tp.CreatedAt,
	}
}

package i18n

import (
	"golang.org/x/text/language"
	"golang.org/x/text/message"
)

var SupportedLanguages = language.NewMatcher([]language.Tag{
	language.English,
	language.Dutch,
	language.French,
	language.German,
	language.Italian,
	language.Japanese,
	language.Korean,
	language.Portuguese,
	language.Russian,
	language.Spanish,
	language.Swedish,
	language.Thai,
	language.Vietnamese,
	language.Malay,
	language.Chinese,
	language.Finnish,
	language.Norwegian,
	language.Danish,
})

func GetLocaleFromHeader(acceptHeader string) language.Tag {
	tags, _, _ := language.ParseAcceptLanguage(acceptHeader)
	locale, _, _ := SupportedLanguages.Match(tags...)
	return locale
}

func Localise(locale language.Tag, text string) string {
	p := message.NewPrinter(locale)

	return p.Sprintf(text)
}
